{
  "stem": "1363.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My word.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, as I told you before, the laws came in every six months, something new that the Jews are not allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish children are not allowed to go to the-- certain schools, because they don't need education or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- we had quite a lot of restrictions by that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the beginning, I don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was before the Hungarian war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was called Omike-- O-M-I-K-E.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a Jewish organization of-- I don't know what the ones in Sydney are, in Australia, Betar-- where they got together on Sunday for a dance, or for going out into the countryside, or having a picnic, or things like that.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember I had-- by that time, I was 14, 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a boyfriend who-- of course, boyfriend in those days was not going to bed with a guy, but to go out, that he came up to your home and asked your mother's permission to take you out to a movie, or to a dance, or to a meal, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a pianist, a very good one on top of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was our group's pianist when we had a, when we had a dancing group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, I always missed out to dance with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he got a radiogram-- is that what they called it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A phonogram.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Phonogram, and put on a few records, and then he just grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went dancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So these were little memory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Klein-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lesley ?] Klein.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did not survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
